column5: Going up to Crane's (Wolsey Bay area) June 7th thru 14th to chase muskies. Just ordered a new 60hp Yamaha for my Alumacraft to scoot around a bit quicker. Anyone else going to be up there?
no but I was up there a couple years ago, nice spot. There's some nice night time eyes close by too.
Right on!!  Awesome ski's up there!
Let a nice one for me ... I'll be at Wolseley Lodge in September.
I'll be in the main channel for the June 7th muskie opener   Also back in Sept/Oct.
